data.description: UPDATES GALORE, HARD TO FIND   4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath ranch home with WALK OUT basement leads to a 14x36 concrete patio and beautiful private yard fully fenced with white vinyl fencing.  The 10x16 shed is included along with the children's play equipment.  Lots of updates including some solid oak doors, 2 main floor bathrooms, one with double sinks. Some new windows with triple pane glass; other are double pane. Main floor bedrooms have sliding barn closet doors. The 18'x13'deck overlooks large private backyard.  25x9 concrete parking pad located next to the 2-car garage.  Pre-Inspected by Ideal Home Inspections on 12/5/23. New flooring in rec room, 4th bedroom plus lower-level walk-out door 2023.
